                <text>hypocentre</text>
            </label>
            <label key="87e5153577e87fb95bc005643fd2068e">
                <text>According to the diagram above, which one of the following statements is correct?</text>
            </label>
            <label key="2061b5a5ee9ae851b0b89ff7ad8fee44">
                <text>The epicentre of the earthquake is at City M.</text>
            </label>
            <label key="f9eda2b155c6865d37c39fd293ec31e0">
